Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.55,0:00:03.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The light of summer is the radiance of yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.46,0:00:05.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the tears lies the legend of the mountain witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:08.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Detective Boys Have found themselves lost\Nwhere the mountain witch is said to dwell!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.51,0:00:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It definitely seems something's\Ngoing to happen tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.15,0:00:11.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.53,0:00:13.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.18,0:00:14.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:11.13,Character Card,,0,0,0,,ROAD\NCLOSED
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.83,0:02:12.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:15.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.17,0:02:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The seventeenth one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.21,0:02:21.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard figuring out the roads around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:25.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of forks and dead ends that aren't on the map...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.69,0:02:27.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I told you to not to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:31.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you said you were going to avoid traffic by taking a side road...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Traffic and heat are a cool engine's biggest enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:42.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought that, even if we did get lost, we could\Njust use the GPS on our cell phones...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:46.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet never expecting that this would be out of the service area.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:48.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you have a GPS installed in your car?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:53.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you did, it could tell us which way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.16,0:02:55.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:58.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Car-mounted GPS systems are still being developed...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:03:00.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'll really be something when they're perfected!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:03.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fully loaded with all kinds of neat functions, they'll be amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:06.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they ever are perfected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:09.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:13.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we keep going, we may be able to find\Nour way back into the service area.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.89,0:03:15.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or at the very least meet some other cars or people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:17.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, it's so hard to figure these places out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:27.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:28.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's completely punctured.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:31.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you bring a spare tire?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:35.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just exchanged these tires out for new ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:37.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I never expected to end up with a flat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:42.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On top of that, we had too much baggage, so if I didn't\Ntake the spare tire out, we couldn't have fit everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:47.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, the sun's already completely set,\Nand we don't know where we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:50.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That being the case, I guess we'll have to camp here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:53.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "Eh"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:55.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We had originally planned to camp out anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:57.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we already have all the camping equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:00.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, this mountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:04.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's kinda creepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like ghosts or monsters could come out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.61,0:04:09.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or even those creatures from the folktales...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:12.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man-eating hags or mountain witches!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:14.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mountain witches!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:15.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way those kinds of monsters actually exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:21.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if you're looking for a house that fits that image...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's one over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, could that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A mountain witch's house...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:35.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiots, as if that were even possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:36.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:41.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it looks like a fairly big house, we should\Nsee if they'll let us stay there for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:45.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's strange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I'm not seeing any other lights in the\Narea, it's probably the only house here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:55.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That such a big house would be alone\Nhere in these mountain recesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:57.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's almost as if it were beckoning us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:03.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saying, "Come here, come here!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:06.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:09.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall we camp here, or shall we ask to stay in that house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:10.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Make a decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:13.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi's scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:16.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But camping out here is dangerous too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:20.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:21.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To the mountain witch's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:27.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, I'll protect both of you with my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:29.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, does that mean you'll be eaten in my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:35.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:40.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, the mountain witch would probably think\NGenta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} would make a better meal, and be tastier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:43.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd make a good soup too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you guys morons?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:45.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:48.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Carry your own things!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:50.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:03.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a fine thatched-roof house!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:06.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look much like a mountain witch's house, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:07.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:12.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because mountain witches seem like\Nthey'd live in small, run-down hovels...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:15.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep, yep, and they hold kitchen knives in their hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:17.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A big kitchen cleaver, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:22.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This sort of kitchen knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It came!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:28.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mountain witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.46,0:06:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma, do you live in this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:32.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:35.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you would let us stay for a night...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:37.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our car got a flat tire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:40.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A flat tire, in these parts?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:43.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse us for the abrupt request...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were headed to the campground\Nwhen we lost our way, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.23,0:06:50.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And just as we were at a loss for what to\Ndo, we happened upon your house...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.03,0:06:51.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:53.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, you should have said so earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:55.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that kitchen knife for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:07:02.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I was cutting pickled vegetables in that\Nshed over there when I heard your voices...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:08.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wondering who it could be in a place like this, I came out and heard\Nyou all talking about what a mountain witch would be like, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:13.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We haven't seen lights from any other\Nnearby houses apart from yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:17.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the only house in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the people that used to live here left to live in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:25.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we can't talk comfortably out here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So if it's all right with you, do come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:29.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:39.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone else living here besides you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:41.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:44.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's another pair of slippers left out...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:51.53,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Those slippers are my grandson Shouta's, who\Nleft this house ten years ago to become a chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:51.40,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tanaka Iwae (74)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:56.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just that I left them there from when he took them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:58.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want to use them, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:02.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are also many slippers over\Nthere in that shoe cupboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:05.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no—I wasn't really asking with that intention...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:08.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:09.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got yours too, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.98,0:08:11.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:12.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder who this person is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:15.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's Shouta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:23.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These past ten years, his letters have all been lacking and he's\Nnever come back to visit me even once—a thoughtless child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:30.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that he's been gaining skill as a chef, though, because\Nhe sends a large amount of money to me every month, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:35.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't touched 1/1000th of a yen\Nof that thoughtless child's money!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.13,0:08:38.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goldfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:40.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are also my grandson's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:43.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leaving such troublesome things...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.43,0:08:46.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But those goldfish are quite large...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:49.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because they've been alive for over ten years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you fattening them up to eat them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:55.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eat this, eat that—Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you're\Nno different from a mountain witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:56.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:00.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Tsuburaya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:04.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just now, from the gap in that door,\Nsomeone was looking this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well now, just who could it be, at a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:11.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:16.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you guys, and what are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:21.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boy, is someone from this house here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:24.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:26.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you call them over here for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:28.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What business do you have with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:30.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:35.12,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We came to this mountain to go on a forest retreat, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:39.24,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We got lost, and ended up running out of gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:43.69,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,If it's all right with you, could we sleep here for the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:35.12,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ooba Akane (25)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:39.26,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Adachi Raito (29)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:43.48,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kahara Fuuga (28)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:49.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, we're not suspicious people or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:51.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Kahara Fuuga!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:53.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Ooba Akane
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.89,0:09:55.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Adachi Raito.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:58.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I work in the service industry in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:01.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'm one of his customers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:05.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you please let us stay for just the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll let you stay for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:10.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a lifesaver!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.48,0:10:13.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I won't have you cross\Nthis threshold a second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:16.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She certainly doesn't seem very welcoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:22.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever, I really didn't want to ask to stay here in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:23.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:25.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You all, don't just stand there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:26.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a seat over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:27.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:30.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't want to harm the mood any further, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:33.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All because Fuuga got lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:36.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So sorry, Milady!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:38.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, at any rate, let's go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:41.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:43.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You two are hosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:50.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm the number two in our\Nshop, and Raito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:54.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to the patronage from milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:57.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goldfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:10:58.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't they super cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:00.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, there sure are a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:02.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a Tamasaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.49,0:11:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tamasaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:05.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, it's this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:08.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one with a body that looks like a\Nryukin, and a tail like that of a mackerel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:13.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Out of these twelve, its the only one of a\Nvariety that you don't get to see very often!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:15.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing, Fuuga sure knows a lot about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:17.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because I used to have goldfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:19.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a stinker!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:20.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, for me, it's rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:23.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ones placed on the right side are quartz...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:26.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The speckled rocks next to them are mica...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:32.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then the shiny black ones on this left side are\Nobsidian, which were used in the Joumon period.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:34.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're both super geniuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:39.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rather than geniuses, wouldn't they just\Nbe called knowledgeable, in this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:41.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's calculating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.53,0:11:46.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doing that and acting dumb so that the men can feel\Ngood about themselves and make a fuss over her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:49.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A type of woman that'll ruin a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.33,0:11:51.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:58.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's all right with you, could I borrow your kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:00.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I had planned to do some rudimentary\Ncooking with these children at the campground...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we brought ingredients for curry and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:09.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:14.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it's a simple dish, I was thinking I could prepare it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:16.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no need for men to be in the kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:22.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's just curry, I can make it as long as you have the ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:24.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, sorry to trouble you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:25.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi will help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:28.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not a matter children need to concern themselves with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:29.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.95,0:12:30.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.49,0:12:33.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never prepared food, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:37.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's just curry, I can make it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:40.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, it's something I often made in the past for my grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are the ingredients?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:43.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're in that bag there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:46.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a large bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:49.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was wondering what he'd brought along.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:12:58.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma's curry was delicious, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} will be happy as long as he gets to eat, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:03.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it really was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The children will use the room on\Nthe right side of that dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:10.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:12.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the menfolk will use the room\Non the left side of this dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:18.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You will use this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:21.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to be in the same room as the two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:25.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Males and females seven years old and\Nabove shall not be behind the same doors!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:25.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:27.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that some sort of incantation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying—you're a young, unmarried woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:31.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's improper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:34.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does that mean, it's "improper"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:35.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're seven years old...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:37.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it still all right to stay in the same room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:39.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi's not married either...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:18.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:27.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's coming from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:30.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think this is the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:46.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Mitsuhiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not even 4 AM yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:52.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please... run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:54.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry... we must...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we don't, we'll be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:02.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That voice just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was that young woman, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:05.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It came from outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Milady!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:14.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Milady!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:16.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:17.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:18.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:19.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:21.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:22.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:24.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An ambulance and the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:27.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:28.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:29.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Raito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:31.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuuga...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:32.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, bring her inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:34.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:40.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:44.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her carotid artery has been slashed with a sharp weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:45.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's lost too much blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:46.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's too late then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:49.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid—don't say such things!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:50.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuuga...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:55.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sharp weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:07.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Normally, it'd be a blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:09.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like a knife or a kitchen knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:12.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But who, and why at this hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And with what sort of blade...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:16.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In these mountain recesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:19.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mountain recesses, and blades...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:22.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mountain witch...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:26.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police and ambulance will both be here in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:28.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:29.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:31.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose you could be thinking that I'm a mountain witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:38.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:40.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would it be all right for me to use the washroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:42.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:45.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As you can imagine, I'd like to get rid of this blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:46.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:51.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the washroom, you go out those shoji doors and\Nit's at the dead end when you turn right at the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:53.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right after the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.37,0:16:56.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, putting together what you all said...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:05.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This morning, at approximately 3:58 AM...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:08.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You suddenly heard a woman's scream\Nand when you went out to take a look...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:12.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You found this woman with her neck slashed, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:14.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:15.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:19.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim's name was Ooba Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, 25 years of age.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:22.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was a loan company president's daughter, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:24.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:26.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so, from what you've said...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:33.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When everyone got to the scene, there was\Nalready someone there next to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:34.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you be the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:37.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:43.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I heard her scream, I was on the first\Nfloor in order to use the restroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:47.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I got to the scene before everyone\Nwho came from the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:51.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, at that time, did you see anyone suspicious there or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:57.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was still quite dark, and I was more\Nconcerned with her, who had collapsed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:01.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, your name is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:03.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Adachi Raito.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.94,0:18:06.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Adachi Raito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kahara Fuuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:12.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kahara Fuuga{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:16.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly, this house was Yamada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:17.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tanaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:19.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the Tanaka house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:23.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am Tanaka Iwae, who reported the crime to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:26.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry—that's right, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:29.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The name of the person who reported the crime\Nis indeed somewhere in my memo book...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:32.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is he really all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:34.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:39.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It occurs to me to ask why Adachi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and\NKahara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} are here in Tanaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s house...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:43.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And also, how you're related to the victim...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.48,0:18:47.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was a customer at the shop that Fuuga and I work at...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:53.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Milady Akane said she wanted to go on\Na forest retreat, so we drove her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're just your ordinary hosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:56.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:57.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:19:01.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, he got lost on the road, and we ran out of gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:06.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last night, we were give permission to\Nstay the night in Tanaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:08.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:10.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tanaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, as far as your family members.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:12.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are none.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:18.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since my grandson left ten years ago, it's just been me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:22.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, for you all, is it the same as usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:24.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same as those guys over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:29.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the way to the campground, we got lost\Nand on top of that our car got a flat tire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:31.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then we asked grandma if we could stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:34.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We got here a bit before those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:39.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it's the same as usual, you've found\Nyourself involved in a case, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.66,0:19:41.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it appears that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:45.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran out of gas, and a flat tire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:49.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.38,0:19:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly, you should get exorcised or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.55,0:19:57.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because there's no doubt you have some\Nsort of sinister thing possessing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:20:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, do you have any clue as\Nfar as the culprit is concerned?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:02.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:09.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though it was raining at the time of the crime, there were no\Nfootprints around the house except for in front of the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:10.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The weapon hasn't been found...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:14.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And to make matters worse, no one\Nwitnessed any suspicious characters, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:16.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit and the weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:20.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would still have to be in this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:24.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.62,0:20:27.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You couldn't be suspecting us, could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:28.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no helping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:33.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were the ones who brought her here after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:33.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, it doesn't mean we are just\Nsuspecting the two of you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:42.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll have to conduct a thorough police interview\Nwith each of you, one by one, about the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:45.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, the one to discover the body, Adachi Raito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:47.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just the name I use at the shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:48.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A thorough police interview...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:52.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How are you going to treat us like criminals even without evidence!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:56.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not necessarily that we're treating you like criminals, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:59.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Fuuga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until some evidence or the weapon presents\Nitself, you won't get one word from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:10.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's fine, but with that attitude you're\Nnot giving off a good impression...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:17.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A saw, a knife, a wide-bladed hatchet, and two kitchen knives...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Agasa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:23.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you bring such a large quantity of weapons with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:24.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's to be expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:26.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since we came intending to camp...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:28.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You two really don't have anything on you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.48,0:21:32.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We just underwent a body search as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, in this house there are three kitchen\Nknives, a hoe, a sickle, an axe, and scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.16,0:21:45.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this really all?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:50.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only thing left is my grandson's\Ntoolbox that's locked up in the shed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:52.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'd imagine they're all rusted by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:21:53.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw it this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.09,0:22:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While I was on the way back to the room from\Nthe restroom, I noticed a strange sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.64,0:22:09.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was coming from the kitchen...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when I peered in...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:15.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This old woman was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.98,0:22:18.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.23,0:22:22.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sharpening a kitchen knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:24.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While her hair moved to and fro...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.49,0:22:26.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A kitchen cleaver with a deep red handle...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:22:29.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With a demonic expression on her face!
